Docs:

FILES   .   	what you are reading
TPATCH  .FOR	short description
TPATCH  .DOC	documentation of the whole package

The patch:

TPATCH  .Z80	source of patch (comments in german, sorry)
TPATCH0 .HEX	for loading over TURBO.COM version 3.00A
TPATCH0 .INS	installation file for patched TURBO.COM
TPATCH1 .HEX	for loading over TURBO.COM version 3.01A
TPATCH1 .INS	installation file for patched TURBO.COM
TURBO   .MSG	original, but includes some forgotten error messages
TURBO   .OVR	new overlay
TURBOVR .INS	installation file for new overlay
TURBOVR .Z80	source of new overlay (comments in german, sorry)

Support of new features:

NAMEDDIR.INC	adds DIR form support
NEWCHAI0.INC	adds improved Chain/Execute procedure, version 3.00A
NEWCHAI1.INC	dito, version 3.01A
NEWCHAIN.SOU	source of NEWCHAIN.INC, for InLass (the InLine-Assembler)
Z3ENV   .INC	defines the structure of the environment descriptor

Utilies:

CHAIN   .PAS	program to let run CHN files, uses include files above
CHAIN0  .INS	installation file for CHAIN.COM, version 3.00A
CHAIN1  .INS	dito, version 3.01A
COMTOCHN.PAS	program to make CHN file from Turbo Pascal COM file
THEINST .DOC	documentation of TheInst (in german, sorry)
THEINST .PAS	general installation program from Olaf Krumnow
